54587616495, \"rank\": 0.40240166004218464, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier, it proved a morning of two mums at the rowing, one delighted and one disappointed.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mathilda Hodgkins-Byrne had not been expected to win a medal but took bronze with Becky Wilde in the double sculls.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathilda_Hodgkins-Byrne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mathilda Hodgkins-Byrne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathilda_Hodgkins-Byrne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathilda_Hodgkins-Byrne\"}, {\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999968437186696, \"rank\": 1.9971390846091376e-06, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was an impressive outcome bearing in mind Wilde had undergone surgery on both forearms back in September and getting to Paris in itself had been seen by the duo as a victory of sorts.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 893, \"end\": 898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999968437186696, \"rank\": 1.9971390846091376e-06, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}, {\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://